---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Articles
description: Clear explanations of finance, technology, and automation.
navKey: articles
---

<section class="page-hero page-hero-compact">
    <p class="eyebrow">Articles</p>

    <h1>Clear explanations for practical decisions.</h1>

    <p class="hero-copy">
        Guides connect related tools, explain what the numbers mean,
        and show when each calculator is useful.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="section section-first">
    {% if collections.articles.length %}
        <div class="card-grid">
            {% for article in collections.articles | reverse %}
                <a class="link-card" href="{{ article.url }}">
                    <h2>{{ article.data.listingTitle or article.data.title }}</h2>

                    <p>
                        {{ article.data.description }}
                    </p>

                    {% if article.data.displayDate %}
                        <small class="card-meta">
                            Published {{ article.data.displayDate }}
                        </small>
                    {% endif %}

                    <span>Read article →</span>
                </a>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    {% else %}
        <div class="content-card empty-state">
            <h2>Articles are coming soon</h2>

            <p>
                New guides will appear here automatically when they are published.
            </p>
        </div>
    {% endif %}
</section>
